                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6973" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1086</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8365 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">他评级，我偿债？——紫光集团信用评级虚高之谜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">He was rated then I repaid the debt? ——The inflation of Unigroup&#39;s credit rating</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵宇恒，叶可婷，雷竞</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">紫光集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信用评级；信用评级主体；偿债主体；集团；主体错配；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">credit rating; rating subject; debt subject; group; subject mismatch</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信用评级是债券市场基础性制度，而我国信用评级体系仍存在评级虚高等问题，阻碍市场高质量发展。本案例主要描述紫光集团信用评级短期内断崖式下降的故事。2014-2019年，头顶清华校企光环、坐拥紫光股份等绩优股的紫光集团，凭借AAA级信用评级，采取激进型债券融资策略，试图构建市值千亿的芯片帝国。然而自2020年起，公司却频频曝出债务违约，信用评级随即在几个月内骤跌至C级，引发一系列消极影响。案例分析紫光集团信用评级虚高原因，旨在引导学生了解信用评级概念与依据、区分公司债券发行的信用评级主体与偿债主体，帮助学生分析合并报表与母公司报表在信用评级中发挥的不同作用，探讨信用评级虚高造成的影响。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Credit rating is the basic of bond market. Our rating system has several problems of inflated ratings hinder the development still. This case describes the short-term decline in the credit rating of Unigroup. From 2014 to 2019 Unigroup with AAA credit rating, having Tsinghua school-enterprise halo and sitting on blue-chip stocks such as Uni shares, adopted aggressive bond financing to build a chip empire with a market value of 100 billion. However, since 2020 its debt defaulted frequently, and its credit rating plummeted to C within months, which triggered negative effects. The case analyzes the reasons for the inflated credit rating, aiming to guide students to understand the concept of credit rating and its basis, distinguish the credit rating subject and debt subject in bond issuance. It helps students analyze influence of consolidated and parent’s statements in credit ratings, with the impact of inflated credit ratings.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信用评级及影响因素；偿债主体与信用评级主体；信用评级虚高的原因；信用评级虛高的影响；提高信用评级准确性的方法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
